I can wait

03:07.755 --> 03:10.258
* When you know
you're always late

03:11.592 --> 03:13.227
* Always late

03:15.896 --> 03:16.930
* With your kisses

03:20.668 --> 03:23.537
* Why, why, why do you want

03:23.571 --> 03:26.740
* To do me this way

