That was Lefty Frizzell's
Always Late With Your Kisses.

03:37.017 --> 03:39.253
Before that,
we heard Buck Owens.

03:40.554 --> 03:42.155
Get your waders out.

03:42.189 --> 03:45.426
It's seven days before
the state officially drowns
Northfork.

03:47.561 --> 03:50.364
It's sunny skies
with the highs being 51...

03:50.964 --> 03:52.700
"To the loving O'Brien family.

03:55.336 --> 03:57.771
"It has been brought
to our attention

03:57.805 --> 04:00.841
"that the remains
of a Mrs. Patricia O'Brien...
[TYPEWRITER CLICKING]

04:02.843 --> 04:04.011
..."have yet to be excavated.

04:06.914 --> 04:08.316
[TYPEWRITER CLICKING]

04:11.319 --> 04:12.486
